probably the most searched for option of formatter :)

Note: `lineEnds.leftCurly` affects all left curlies, there are specialised options for
different curly places (e.g. `lineEnds.blockCurly`, `lineEnds.objectLiteralCurly`, etc.)
see [haxeflixel style sample](#codesamples.CommonSamples.haxeflixel_style)

---

{
    "lineEnds": {
        "leftCurly": "both",
		"emptyCurly": "break"
    }
}

---

class Main {
    public function new () {}

    public function foo (param1:Int) {
		trace(param1);
		var obj = {
			x:100,
			y:100,
			z:100
			};
	}
}
